#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:53
msgid ""
"Show only databases matching the first subdomain after ``www``: for example "
"the database \"mycompany\" will be shown if the incoming request was sent to "
"``www.mycompany.com`` or ``mycompany.co.uk``, but not for "
"``www2.mycompany.com`` or ``helpdesk.mycompany.com``."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži samo baze, ki se ujemajo s prvo poddomena za ``www``: na primer baza "
"„mycompany“ bo prikazana, če je bil dohodni zahtevek poslan na "
"``www.mycompany.com`` ali ``mycompany.co.uk``, ne pa za "
"``www2.mycompany.com`` ali ``helpdesk.mycompany.com``."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:67
msgid ""
"Setting a proper :option:`--db-filter <odoo-bin --db-filter>` is an "
"important part of securing your deployment. Once it is correctly working and "
"only matching a single database per hostname, it is strongly recommended to "
"block access to the database manager screens, and to use the ``--no-database-"
"list`` startup parameter to prevent listing your databases, and to block "
"access to the database management screens. See also security_."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev ustreznega :option:`--db-filter <odoo-bin --db-filter>` je "
"pomemben del zaščite vaše namestitve. Ko pravilno deluje in se ujema samo z "
"eno bazo na gostitelja, je močno priporočljivo blokirati dostop do zaslonov "
"upravljavca baz podatkov in uporabiti zažgalni parameter ``--no-database-"
"list``, da preprečite izpis vaših baz in blokirate dostop do zaslonov "
"upravljanja baz podatkov. Glejte tudi security_."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:76
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:193
msgid "PostgreSQL"
msgstr "PostgreSQL"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:78
msgid ""
"By default, PostgreSQL only allows connection over UNIX sockets and loopback "
"connections (from \"localhost\", the same machine the PostgreSQL server is "
"installed on)."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto PostgreSQL dovoljuje povezave samo prek vtičev UNIX in povratnih "
"povezav (iz \"localhost\", istega računalnika, na katerem je nameščen "
"strežnik PostgreSQL)."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:82
msgid ""
"UNIX socket is fine if you want Odoo and PostgreSQL to execute on the same "
"machine, and is the default when no host is provided, but if you want Odoo "
"and PostgreSQL to execute on different machines [#different-machines]_ it "
"will need to `listen to network interfaces`_ [#remote-socket]_, either:"
msgstr ""
"Vtič UNIX je v redu, če želite, da se Odoo in PostgreSQL izvajata na istem "
"računalniku, in je privzeta možnost, ko ni navedena nobena gostiteljska "
"naprava, vendar če želite, da se Odoo in PostgreSQL izvajata na različnih "
"računalnikih [#different-machines]_, bo moral `poslušati omrežne vmesnike`_ "
"[#remote-socket]_, bodisi:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:87
msgid ""
"Only accept loopback connections and `use an SSH tunnel`_ between the "
"machine on which Odoo runs and the one on which PostgreSQL runs, then "
"configure Odoo to connect to its end of the tunnel"
msgstr ""
"Sprejemati samo povratne povezave in `uporabiti tunel SSH`_ med "
"računalnikom, na katerem se izvaja Odoo, in tistim, na katerem se izvaja "
"PostgreSQL, nato pa konfigurirati Odoo, da se poveže na svoj konec tunela"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:90
msgid ""
"Accept connections to the machine on which Odoo is installed, possibly over "
"ssl (see `PostgreSQL connection settings`_ for details), then configure Odoo "
"to connect over the network"
msgstr ""
"Sprejemati povezave do računalnika, na katerem je nameščen Odoo, morda prek "
"ssl (podrobnosti v `nastavitvah povezave PostgreSQL`_), nato pa "
"konfigurirati Odoo, da se poveže prek omrežja"

