#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:119
msgid "Configuring Odoo"
msgstr "Konfiguracija Odoo"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:121
msgid ""
"Out of the box, Odoo connects to a local postgres over UNIX socket via port "
"5432. This can be overridden using :ref:`the database options <reference/"
"cmdline/server/database>` when your Postgres deployment is not local and/or "
"does not use the installation defaults."
msgstr ""
"Odoo se takoj po namestitvi poveže z lokalnim postgres prek vtiča UNIX na "
"vratih 5432. To lahko preglasujete z uporabo :ref:`možnosti zbirke podatkov "
"<reference/cmdline/server/database>`, ko vaša namestitev Postgres ni lokalna "
"in/ali ne uporablja privzetih nastavitev namestitve."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:126
msgid ""
"The :doc:`packaged installers <packages>` will automatically create a new "
"user (``odoo``) and set it as the database user."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Paketni namestitveni programi <packages>` bodo samodejno ustvarili "
"novega uporabnika (``odoo``) in ga nastavili kot uporabnika zbirke podatkov."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:129
msgid ""
"The database management screens are protected by the ``admin_passwd`` "
"setting. This setting can only be set using configuration files, and is "
"simply checked before performing database alterations. It should be set to a "
"randomly generated value to ensure third parties can not use this interface."
msgstr ""
"Zasloni za upravljanje zbirk podatkov so zaščiteni z nastavitvijo "
"``admin_passwd``. Ta nastavitev je mogoče nastaviti samo s konfiguracijske "
"datoteke in se preprosto preveri pred izvajanjem sprememb zbirke podatkov. "
"Nastavljena mora biti na naključno ustvarjeno vrednost, da tretje osebe ne "
"morejo uporabljati tega vmesnika."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:134
msgid ""
"All database operations use the :ref:`database options <reference/cmdline/"
"server/database>`, including the database management screen. For the "
"database management screen to work requires that the PostgreSQL user have "
"``createdb`` right."
msgstr ""
"Vse operacije zbirke podatkov uporabljajo :ref:`možnosti zbirke podatkov "
"<reference/cmdline/server/database>`, vključno z zaslonom za upravljanje "
"zbirke podatkov. Da zaslon za upravljanje zbirke podatkov deluje, mora imeti "
"uporabnik PostgreSQL pravico ``createdb``."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:138
msgid ""
"Users can always drop databases they own. For the database management screen "
"to be completely non-functional, the PostgreSQL user needs to be created "
"with ``no-createdb`` and the database must be owned by a different "
"PostgreSQL user."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki lahko vedno izbrišejo zbirke podatkov, ki so v njihovi lasti. Da "
"zaslon za upravljanje zbirke podatkov postane popolnoma nefunkcionalen, mora "
"biti uporabnik PostgreSQL ustvarjen z ``no-createdb`` in zbirka podatkov "
"mora biti v lasti drugega uporabnika PostgreSQL."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:142
msgid "the PostgreSQL user *must not* be a superuser"
msgstr "uporabnik PostgreSQL *ne sme* biti nadupravitelj"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:147
msgid "connect to a PostgreSQL server on 192.168.1.2"
msgstr "povezava s strežnikom PostgreSQL na 192.168.1.2"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:148
msgid "port 5432"
msgstr "vrata 5432"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:149
msgid "using an 'odoo' user account,"
msgstr "z uporabo uporabniškega računa 'odoo',"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:150
msgid "with 'pwd' as a password"
msgstr "s 'pwd' kot geslom"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:151
msgid "filtering only db with a name beginning with 'mycompany'"
msgstr "filtriranje samo podatkovnih baz z imenom, ki se začne z 'mycompany'"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:168
msgid "SSL Between Odoo and PostgreSQL"
msgstr "SSL med Odoo in PostgreSQL"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:170
msgid ""
"Since Odoo 11.0, you can enforce ssl connection between Odoo and PostgreSQL. "
"in Odoo the db_sslmode control the ssl security of the connection with value "
"chosen out of 'disable', 'allow', 'prefer', 'require', 'verify-ca' or "
"'verify-full'"
msgstr ""
"Od Odoo 11.0 naprej lahko uveljavljate SSL povezavo med Odoo in PostgreSQL. "
"V Odoo db_sslmode nadzoruje SSL varnost povezave z vrednostjo, izbrano izmed "
"'disable', 'allow', 'prefer', 'require', 'verify-ca' ali 'verify-full'"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:175
msgid ""
"`PostgreSQL Doc <https://www.postgresql.org/docs/12/static/libpq-ssl.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"`PostgreSQL dokumentacija <https://www.postgresql.org/docs/12/static/libpq-"
"ssl.html>`_"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:180
msgid "Builtin server"
msgstr "Vgrajen strežnik"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:182
msgid ""
"Odoo includes built-in HTTP, cron, and live-chat servers, using either multi-"
"threading or multi-processing."
msgstr ""
"Odoo vključuje vgrajene HTTP, cron in live-chat strežnike, ki uporabljajo "
"večnitnost ali večprocesnost."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:185
msgid ""
"The **multi-threaded** server is a simpler server primarily used for "
"development, demonstrations, and its compatibility with various operating "
"systems (including Windows). A new thread is spawned for every new HTTP "
"request, even for long-lived connections such as websocket. Extra daemonic "
"cron threads are spawned too. Due to a Python limitation (GIL), it doesn't "
"make the best use of the hardware."
msgstr ""
"**Večnitni** strežnik je preprostejši strežnik, ki se uporablja predvsem za "
"razvoj, predstavitve in združljivost z različnimi operacijskimi sistemi "
"(vključno z Windows). Nova nit se ustvari za vsako novo HTTP zahtevo, tudi "
"za dolgotrajne povezave, kot so websocket. Ustvarjene so tudi dodatne daemon "
"cron niti. Zaradi omejitve Pythona (GIL) ne izkorišča najbolje strojne "
"opreme."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:191
msgid ""
"The multi-threaded server is the default server, also for docker containers. "
"It is selected by leaving the :option:`--workers <odoo-bin --workers>` "
"option out or setting it to ``0``."
msgstr ""
"Večnitni strežnik je privzeti strežnik, tudi za docker konteinerje. Izbere "
"se tako, da izpustite možnost :option:`--workers <odoo-bin --workers>` ali "
"jo nastavite na ``0``."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:194
msgid ""
"The **multi-processing** server is a full-blown server primarily used for "
"production. It is not liable to the same Python limitation (GIL) on resource "
"usage and hence makes the best use of the hardware. A pool of workers is "
"created upon server startup. New HTTP requests are queued by the OS until "
"there are workers ready to process them. An extra event-driven HTTP worker "
"for the live chat is spawned on an alternative port. Extra cron workers are "
"spawned too. A configurable process reaper monitors resource usage and can "
"kill/restart failed workers."
msgstr ""
"**Večprocesni** strežnik je polno razvit strežnik, ki se uporablja predvsem "
"v produkciji. Ni podvržen isti omejitvi Pythona (GIL) glede porabe virov in "
"zato najbolje izkorišča strojno opremo. Bazen delavcev se ustvari ob zagonu "
"strežnika. Nove HTTP zahteve čakajo v vrsti OS, dokler niso delavci "
"pripravljeni za njihovo obdelavo. Dodaten dogodkovno-gnani HTTP delavec za "
"live chat se ustvari na alternativnih vratih. Ustvarjeni so tudi dodatni "
"cron delavci. Nastavljiv nadzornik procesov spremlja porabo virov in lahko "
"ustavi/ponovno zažene spodletele delavce."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:201
msgid ""
"The multi-processing server is opt-in. It is selected by setting "
"the :option:`--workers <odoo-bin --workers>` option to a non-null integer."
msgstr ""
"Večprocesni strežnik je opcijski. Izbere se tako, da nastavite "
"možnost :option:`--workers <odoo-bin --workers>` na celo število, ki ni nič."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:205
msgid ""
"Because it is highly customized for Linux servers, the multi-processing "
"server is not available on Windows."
msgstr ""
"Ker je zelo prilagojen za Linux strežnike, večprocesni strežnik ni na voljo "
"v Windows."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:209
msgid "Worker number calculation"
msgstr "Izračun števila delavcev"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:211
msgid "Rule of thumb : (#CPU * 2) + 1"
msgstr "Pravilo palca: (#CPU * 2) + 1"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:212
msgid "Cron workers need CPU"
msgstr "Cron delavci potrebujejo CPU"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:213
msgid "1 worker ~= 6 concurrent users"
msgstr "1 delavec ~= 6 sočasnih uporabnikov"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:216
msgid "memory size calculation"
msgstr "izračun velikosti pomnilnika"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:218
msgid ""
"We consider 20% of the requests are heavy requests, while 80% are simpler "
"ones"
msgstr ""
"Upoštevamo, da je 20% zahtev težkih zahtev, medtem ko je 80% preprostejših"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:219
msgid ""
"A heavy worker, when all computed field are well designed, SQL requests are "
"well designed, ... is estimated to consume around 1GB of RAM"
msgstr ""
"Težji delavec, ko so vsa izračunana polja dobro zasnovana, SQL zahteve so "
"dobro zasnovane, ... naj bi porabil približno 1GB RAM"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:220
msgid ""
"A lighter worker, in the same scenario, is estimated to consume around 150MB "
"of RAM"
msgstr "Lažji delavec, v istem scenariju, naj bi porabil približno 150MB RAM"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:222
msgid ""
"Needed RAM = #worker * ( (light_worker_ratio * light_worker_ram_estimation) "
"+ (heavy_worker_ratio * heavy_worker_ram_estimation) )"
msgstr ""
"Potrebni RAM = #worker * ( (light_worker_ratio * "
"light_worker_ram_estimation) + (heavy_worker_ratio * "
"heavy_worker_ram_estimation) )"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:225
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:413
msgid "LiveChat"
msgstr "LiveChat"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:227
msgid ""
"In multi-processing, a dedicated LiveChat worker is automatically started "
"and listens on the :option:`--gevent-port <odoo-bin --gevent-port>`. By "
"default, the HTTP requests will keep accessing the normal HTTP workers "
"instead of the LiveChat one. You must deploy a proxy in front of Odoo and "
"redirect incoming requests whose path starts with ``/websocket/`` to the "
"LiveChat worker. You must also start Odoo in :option:`--proxy-mode <odoo-bin "
"--proxy-mode>` so it uses the real client headers (such as hostname, scheme, "
"and IP) instead of the proxy ones."
msgstr ""
"Pri večopravilnosti se samodejno zažene namenski delavec LiveChat, ki "
"posluša na :option:`--gevent-port <odoo-bin --gevent-port>`. Privzeto bodo "
"zahteve HTTP še naprej dostopale do navadnih delavcev HTTP namesto do "
"delavca LiveChat. Pred Odoo morate namestiti posredniški strežnik in "
"preusmeriti prihajajoče zahteve, katerih pot se začne z ``/websocket/``, na "
"delavca LiveChat. Odoo morate tudi zagnati v načinu :option:`--proxy-mode "
"<odoo-bin --proxy-mode>`, da uporablja prave glave odjemalca (kot so ime "
"gostitelja, shema in IP) namesto posredniških."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:237
msgid "Server with 4 CPU, 8 Thread"
msgstr "Strežnik s 4 CPU, 8 nitmi"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:238
msgid "60 concurrent users"
msgstr "60 sočasnih uporabnikov"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:240
msgid "60 users / 6 = 10 <- theoretical number of worker needed"
msgstr "60 uporabnikov / 6 = 10 <- teoretično število potrebnih delavcev"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:241
msgid "(4 * 2) + 1 = 9 <- theoretical maximal number of worker"
msgstr "(4 * 2) + 1 = 9 <- teoretično največje število delavcev"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:242
msgid ""
"We'll use 8 workers + 1 for cron. We'll also use a monitoring system to "
"measure cpu load, and check if it's between 7 and 7.5 ."
msgstr ""
"Uporabili bomo 8 delavcev + 1 za cron. Uporabili bomo tudi sistem za nadzor, "
"da izmerimo obremenitev procesorja in preverimo, ali je med 7 in 7,5."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:243
msgid "RAM = 9 * ((0.8*150) + (0.2*1024)) ~= 3GB RAM for Odoo"
msgstr "RAM = 9 * ((0,8*150) + (0,2*1024)) ~= 3 GB RAM za Odoo"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:245
msgid "in :ref:`the configuration file <reference/cmdline/config_file>`:"
msgstr "v :ref:`konfiguracijski datoteki <reference/cmdline/config_file>`:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:261
msgid "HTTPS"
msgstr "HTTPS"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:263
msgid ""
"Whether it's accessed via website/web client or web service, Odoo transmits "
"authentication information in cleartext. This means a secure deployment of "
"Odoo must use HTTPS\\ [#switching]_. SSL termination can be implemented via "
"just about any SSL termination proxy, but requires the following setup:"
msgstr ""
"Ne glede na to, ali se do Odoo dostopa prek spletnega mesta/spletnega "
"odjemalca ali spletne storitve, Odoo prenaša preveritvene podatke v "
"nezaščitenem besedilu. To pomeni, da mora varna namestitev Odoo uporabljati "
"HTTPS\\ [#switching]_. Zaključevanje SSL je mogoče izvesti prek skoraj "
"katerega koli posredniškega strežnika za zaključevanje SSL, vendar zahteva "
"naslednjo nastavitev:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:268
msgid ""
"Enable Odoo's :option:`proxy mode <odoo-bin --proxy-mode>`. This should only "
"be enabled when Odoo is behind a reverse proxy"
msgstr ""
"Omogočite Odoo-v :option:`posredniški način <odoo-bin --proxy-mode>`. To naj "
"bo omogočeno samo, kadar je Odoo za povratnim posredniškim strežnikom"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:269
msgid "Set up the SSL termination proxy (`Nginx termination example`_)"
msgstr ""
"Nastavite posredniški strežnik za zaključevanje SSL (`primer zaključevanja "
"Nginx`_)"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:270
msgid "Set up the proxying itself (`Nginx proxying example`_)"
msgstr ""
"Nastavite sam posredniški prenos (`primer posredniškega prenosa Nginx`_)"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:271
msgid ""
"Your SSL termination proxy should also automatically redirect non-secure "
"connections to the secure port"
msgstr ""
"Vaš posredniški strežnik za zaključevanje SSL naj tudi samodejno preusmeri "
"nezavarovane povezave na varni vhod"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:277
msgid "Redirect http requests to https"
msgstr "Preusmeri zahteve http na https"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:278
msgid "Proxy requests to odoo"
msgstr "Posredniške zahteve na odoo"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:286
msgid "in ``/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/odoo.conf`` set:"
msgstr "v ``/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/odoo.conf`` nastavite:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:362
msgid "HTTPS Hardening"
msgstr "Utrjevanje HTTPS"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:364
msgid ""
"Add the `Strict-Transport-Security` header to all requests, in order to "
"prevent browsers from ever sending a plain HTTP request to this domain. You "
"will need to maintain a working HTTPS service with a valid certificate on "
"this domain at all times, otherwise your users will see security alerts or "
"be entirely unable to access it."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte glavo `Strict-Transport-Security` vsem zahtevam, da preprečite "
"brskalnikom, da bi kdaj poslali navaden HTTP zahtevek tej domeni. Vzdrževati "
"boste morali delujoč HTTPS servis z veljavnim certifikatom na tej domeni ves "
"čas, sicer bodo vaši uporabniki videli varnostna opozorila ali pa sploh ne "
"bodo mogli dostopati do nje."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:370
msgid ""
"Force HTTPS connections during a year for every visitor in NGINX with the "
"line:"
msgstr ""
"Prisilite HTTPS povezave za leto dni za vsakega obiskovalca v NGINX z "
"vrstico:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:376
msgid ""
"Additional configuration can be defined for the `session_id` cookie. The "
"`Secure` flag can be added to ensure it is never transmitted over HTTP and "
"`SameSite=Lax` to prevent authenticated `CSRF`_."
msgstr ""
"Za piškotek `session_id` je mogoče določiti dodatno konfiguracijo. Dodana je "
"lahko zastavica `Secure`, da zagotovi, da ni nikoli poslan preko HTTP, in "
"`SameSite=Lax`, da prepreči avtenticirani `CSRF`_."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:387
msgid "Odoo as a WSGI Application"
msgstr "Odoo kot WSGI aplikacija"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:389
msgid ""
"It is also possible to mount Odoo as a standard WSGI_ application. Odoo "
"provides the base for a WSGI launcher script as ``odoo-wsgi.example.py``. "
"That script should be customized (possibly after copying it from the setup "
"directory) to correctly set the configuration directly "
"in :mod:`odoo.tools.config` rather than through the command-line or a "
"configuration file."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je tudi namestiti Odoo kot standardno WSGI_ aplikacijo. Odoo "
"zagotavlja osnovo za WSGI skript za zagon kot ``odoo-wsgi.example.py``. Ta "
"skript je treba prilagoditi (po potrebi po kopiranju iz namestitvenega "
"imenika), da pravilno nastavi konfiguracijo neposredno "
"v :mod:`odoo.tools.config` namesto prek ukazne vrstice ali konfiguracijske "
"datoteke."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:395
msgid ""
"However the WSGI server will only expose the main HTTP endpoint for the web "
"client, website and webservice API. Because Odoo does not control the "
"creation of workers anymore it can not setup cron or livechat workers"
msgstr ""
"Vendar bo strežnik WSGI izpostavil samo glavno HTTP končno točko za "
"spletnega odjemalca, spletno mesto in API spletne storitve. Ker Odoo ne "
"nadzoruje več ustvarjanja delavcev, ne more nastaviti cron ali livechat "
"delavcev"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:400
msgid "Cron Workers"
msgstr "Cron delavci"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:402
msgid ""
"Starting one of the built-in Odoo servers next to the WSGI server is "
"required to process cron jobs. That server must be configured to only "
"process crons and not HTTP requests using the :option:`--no-http <odoo-bin --"
"no-http>` cli option or the ``http_enable = False`` configuration file "
"setting."
msgstr ""
"Za obdelavo cron opravil je potrebno zagnati enega od vgrajenih Odoo "
"strežnikov poleg WSGI strežnika. Ta strežnik mora biti konfiguriran tako, da "
"obdeluje samo crone in ne HTTP zahtevkov z uporabo možnosti ukazne "
"vrstice :option:`--no-http <odoo-bin --no-http>` ali nastavitve "
"konfiguracijske datoteke ``http_enable = False``."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:407
msgid ""
"On Linux-like systems, using the multi-processing server over the multi-"
"threading one is recommended to benefit from better hardware usage and "
"increased stability, i.e., using the :option:`--workers=-1 <odoo-bin --"
"workers>` and :option:`--max-cron-threads=n <odoo-bin --max-cron-threads>` "
"cli options."
msgstr ""
"V sistemih, podobnih Linuxu, je priporočljivo uporabiti večprocesni strežnik "
"namesto večnitnega, da izkoristite boljšo uporabo strojne opreme in večjo "
"stabilnost, tj. z uporabo možnosti ukazne vrstice :option:`--workers=-1 "
"<odoo-bin --workers>` in :option:`--max-cron-threads=n <odoo-bin --max-cron-"
"threads>`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:415
msgid ""
"Using a gevent-compatible WSGI server is required for the correct operation "
"of the live chat feature. That server should be able to handle many "
"simultaneous long-lived connections but doesn't need a lot of processing "
"power. All requests whose path starts with ``/websocket/`` should be "
"directed to that server. A regular (thread/process-based) WSGI server should "
"be used for all other requests."
msgstr ""
"Za pravilno delovanje funkcije klepeta v živo je potreben WSGI strežnik, "
"združljiv z gevent. Ta strežnik bi moral biti sposoben obravnavati veliko "
"hkratnih dolgotrajnih povezav, ne potrebuje pa veliko procesorske moči. Vse "
"zahtevke, katerih pot se začne z ``/websocket/``, je treba usmeriti na ta "
"strežnik. Za vse druge zahtevke je treba uporabiti običajen (na nitih/"
"procesih temelječ) WSGI strežnik."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:421
msgid ""
"The Odoo cron server can also be used to serve the live chat requests. Just "
"drop the :option:`--no-http <odoo-bin --no-http>` cli option from the cron "
"server and make sure requests whose path starts with ``/websocket/`` are "
"directed to this server, either on the :option:`--http-port <odoo-bin --http-"
"port>` (multi-threading server) or on the :option:`--gevent-port <odoo-bin --"
"gevent-port>` (multi-processing server)."
msgstr ""
"Strežnik Odoo cron se lahko uporabi tudi za strežbo zahtevkov za klepet v "
"živo. Preprosto opustite možnost ukazne vrstice :option:`--no-http <odoo-bin "
"--no-http>` s cron strežnika in zagotovite, da so zahtevki, katerih pot se "
"začne z ``/websocket/``, usmerjeni na ta strežnik, bodisi na :option:`--http-"
"port <odoo-bin --http-port>` (večnitni strežnik) ali na :option:`--gevent-"
"port <odoo-bin --gevent-port>` (večprocesni strežnik)."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:430
msgid "Serving static files and attachments"
msgstr "Strežba statičnih datotek in prilog"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:432
msgid ""
"For development convenience, Odoo directly serves all static files and "
"attachments in its modules. This may not be ideal when it comes to "
"performances, and static files should generally be served by a static HTTP "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Zaradi priročnosti pri razvoju Odoo neposredno streže vse statične datoteke "
"in priloge v svojih modulih. To morda ni idealno glede zmogljivosti in "
"statične datoteke bi moral na splošno streči statični HTTP strežnik."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:437
msgid "Serving static files"
msgstr "Strežba statičnih datotek"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:439
msgid ""
"Odoo static files are located in each module's :file:`static/` folder, so "
"static files can be served by intercepting all requests to :samp:`/{MODULE}/"
"static/{FILE}`, and looking up the right module (and file) in the various "
"addons paths."
msgstr ""
"Statične datoteke Odoo se nahajajo v mapi :file:`static/` vsakega modula, "
"zato je mogoče statične datoteke streči z prestrezanjem vseh zahtevkov "
"za :samp:`/{MODULE}/static/{FILE}` in iskanjem pravega modula (in datoteke) "
"v različnih poteh dodatkov."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:443
msgid ""
"It is recommended to set the ``Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'none'`` "
"header on all images delivered by the web server. It is not strictly "
"necessary as users cannot modify/inject content inside of "
"modules' :file:`static/` folder and existing images are final (they do not "
"fetch new resources by themselves). However, it is good practice."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je nastaviti glavo ``Content-Security-Policy: default-src "
"'none'`` na vse slike, ki jih dostavi spletni strežnik. To ni strogo "
"potrebno, saj uporabniki ne morejo spreminjati/injicirati vsebine v "
"mapo :file:`static/` modulov in obstoječe slike so končne (ne pridobivajo "
"novih virov same po sebi). Vendar je to dobra praksa."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:448
msgid ""
"Using the above NGINX (https) configuration, the following ``map`` and "
"``location`` blocks should be added to serve static files via NGINX."
msgstr ""
"Z zgornjo konfiguracijo NGINX (https) je treba dodati naslednje bloke "
"``map`` in ``location``, da se statične datoteke strežejo prek NGINX."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:475
msgid ""
"The actual ``root`` and ``try_files`` directives are dependant on your "
"installation, specifically on your :option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin --addons-"
"path>`."
msgstr ""
"Dejanski direktivi ``root`` in ``try_files`` sta odvisni od vaše namestitve, "
"posebej od vašega :option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin --addons-path>`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:482
msgid "Debian package"
msgstr "Paket Debian"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:484
msgid ""
"Say Odoo has been installed via the **debian packages** for Community and "
"Enterprise, and that the :option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin --addons-path>` is "
"``'/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages/odoo/addons'``."
msgstr ""
"Recimo, da je bil Odoo nameščen prek **debian paketov** za Community in "
"Enterprise in da je :option:`--addons-path <odoo-bin --addons-path>` ``'/usr/"
"lib/python3/dist-packages/odoo/addons'``."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:488
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:502
msgid "The ``root`` and ``try_files`` should be:"
msgstr "``root`` in ``try_files`` bi morala biti:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:495
msgid "Git sources"
msgstr "Viri Git"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:497
msgid ""
"Say Odoo has been installed via the **sources**, that both the Community and "
"Enterprise git repositories were cloned in :file:`/opt/odoo/community` "
"and :file:`/opt/odoo/enterprise` respectively, and that the :option:`--"
"addons-path <odoo-bin --addons-path>` is ``'/opt/odoo/community/odoo/addons,/"
"opt/odoo/community/addons,/opt/odoo/enterprise'``."
msgstr ""
"Recimo, da je bil Odoo nameščen prek **virov**, da sta bili zbirki skupnosti "
"(Community) in poslovne (Enterprise) klonirani v :file:`/opt/odoo/community` "
"oziroma :file:`/opt/odoo/enterprise`, in da je :option:`--addons-path <odoo-"
"bin --addons-path>` nastavljen na ``'/opt/odoo/community/odoo/addons,/opt/"
"odoo/community/addons,/opt/odoo/enterprise'``."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:510
msgid "Serving attachments"
msgstr "Posredovanje prilog"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:512
msgid ""
"Attachments are files stored in the filestore which access is regulated by "
"Odoo. They cannot be directly accessed via a static web server as accessing "
"them requires multiple lookups in the database to determine where the files "
"are stored and whether the current user can access them or not."
msgstr ""
"Priloge so datoteke, shranjene v datotečnem prostoru, do katerih dostop "
"ureja Odoo. Do njih ni mogoče neposredno dostopati prek statičnega spletnega "
"strežnika, saj dostop do njih zahteva več poizvedb v bazi podatkov, da se "
"ugotovi, kje so datoteke shranjene in ali ima trenutni uporabnik do njih "
"dostop ali ne."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:517
msgid ""
"Nevertheless, once the file has been located and the access rights verified "
"by Odoo, it is a good idea to serve the file using the static web server "
"instead of Odoo. For Odoo to delegate serving files to the static web "
"server, the `X-Sendfile <https://tn123.org/mod_xsendfile/>`_ (apache) or X-"
"Accel (nginx) extensions must be enabled and configured on the static web "
"server. Once it is set up, start Odoo with the :option:`--x-sendfile <odoo-"
"bin --x-sendfile>` CLI flag (this unique flag is used for both X-Sendfile "
"and X-Accel)."
msgstr ""
"Kljub temu je po tem, ko je datoteka najdena in Odoo preveri dostopne "
"pravice, dobro, da datoteko streže statični spletni strežnik namesto Odooja. "
"Če želite, da Odoo prenese streženje datotek na statični spletni strežnik, "
"morate na statičnem spletnem strežniku omogočiti in konfigurirati razširitvi "
"`X-Sendfile <https://tn123.org/mod_xsendfile/>`_ (apache) ali X-Accel "
"(nginx). Ko je nastavljeno, zaženite Odoo z zastavico CLI :option:`--x-"
"sendfile <odoo-bin --x-sendfile>` (ta enotna zastavica se uporablja tako za "
"X-Sendfile kot za X-Accel)."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:526
msgid ""
"The X-Sendfile extension for apache (and compatible web servers) does not "
"require any supplementary configuration."
msgstr ""
"Razširitev X-Sendfile za apache (in združljive spletne strežnike) ne zahteva "
"nobene dodatne konfiguracije."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:528
msgid ""
"The X-Accel extension for NGINX **does** require the following additionnal "
"configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Razširitev X-Accel za NGINX **pa** zahteva naslednjo dodatno konfiguracijo:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:539
msgid ""
"In case you don't know what is the path to your filestore, start Odoo with "
"the :option:`--x-sendfile <odoo-bin --x-sendfile>` option and navigate to "
"the ``/web/filestore`` URL directly via Odoo (don't navigate to the URL via "
"NGINX). This logs a warnings, the message contains the configuration you "
"need."
msgstr ""
"Če ne veste, kakšna je pot do vašega datotečnega prostora, zaženite Odoo z "
"možnostjo :option:`--x-sendfile <odoo-bin --x-sendfile>` in neposredno prek "
"Oodooja (ne prek NGINX) se pomaknite na URL ``/web/filestore``. To zabeleži "
"opozorilo, sporočilo vsebuje konfiguracijo, ki jo potrebujete."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:548
msgid "Security"
msgstr "Varnost"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:550
msgid ""
"For starters, keep in mind that securing an information system is a "
"continuous process, not a one-shot operation. At any moment, you will only "
"be as secure as the weakest link in your environment."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek imejte v mislih, da je zavarovanje informacijskega sistema stalen "
"proces, ne enkratna operacija. V vsakem trenutku boste varni le toliko, "
"kolikor je varen najšibkejši člen v vašem okolju."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:554
msgid ""
"So please do not take this section as the ultimate list of measures that "
"will prevent all security problems. It's only intended as a summary of the "
"first important things you should be sure to include in your security action "
"plan. The rest will come from best security practices for your operating "
"system and distribution, best practices in terms of users, passwords, and "
"access control management, etc."
msgstr ""
"Zato tega razdelka ne jemljite kot dokončnega seznama ukrepov, ki bodo "
"preprečili vse varnostne težave. Namenjen je le kot povzetek prvih pomembnih "
"stvari, za katere morate poskrbeti, da so vključene v vaš varnostni akcijski "
"načrt. Ostalo bo izhajalo iz najboljših varnostnih praks za vaš operacijski "
"sistem in distribucijo, najboljših praks glede uporabnikov, gesel in "
"upravljanja nadzora dostopa itd."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:560
msgid ""
"When deploying an internet-facing server, please be sure to consider the "
"following security-related topics:"
msgstr ""
"Pri uvajanju strežnika, dostopnega prek interneta, se prepričajte, da "
"upoštevate naslednje varnostne teme:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:563
msgid ""
"Always set a strong super-admin admin password, and restrict access to the "
"database management pages as soon as the system is set up. "
"See :ref:`db_manager_security`."
msgstr ""
"Vedno nastavite močno skrbniško geslo super-admin in omejite dostop do "
"strani za upravljanje baz podatkov takoj, ko je sistem nastavljen. Glejte "
":ref:`db_manager_security`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:566
msgid ""
"Choose unique logins and strong passwords for all administrator accounts on "
"all databases. Do not use 'admin' as the login. Do not use those logins for "
"day-to-day operations, only for controlling/managing the installation. "
"*Never* use any default passwords like admin/admin, even for test/staging "
"databases."
msgstr ""
"Izberite edinstvene prijave in močna gesla za vse skrbniške račune v vseh "
"bazah podatkov. Ne uporabljajte 'admin' kot prijave. Ne uporabljajte teh "
"prijav za vsakodnevne operacije, temveč samo za nadzor/upravljanje "
"namestitve. *Nikoli* ne uporabljajte privzetih gesel, kot je admin/admin, "
"niti za testne/pripravljalne baze podatkov."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:571
msgid ""
"Do **not** install demo data on internet-facing servers. Databases with demo "
"data contain default logins and passwords that can be used to get into your "
"systems and cause significant trouble, even on staging/dev systems."
msgstr ""
"**Ne** nameščajte predstavitvenih podatkov na strežnikih, dostopnih prek "
"interneta. Baze podatkov s predstavitvenimi podatki vsebujejo privzete "
"prijave in gesla, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti za dostop do vaših sistemov in "
"povzročiti znatne težave, tudi v pripravljalnih/razvojnih sistemih."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:575
msgid ""
"Use appropriate database filters ( :option:`--db-filter <odoo-bin --db-"
"filter>`) to restrict the visibility of your databases according to the "
"hostname. See :ref:`dbfilter`. You may also use :option:`-d <odoo-bin -d>` "
"to provide your own (comma-separated) list of available databases to filter "
"from, instead of letting the system fetch them all from the database backend."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ustrezne filtre baz podatkov (:option:`--db-filter <odoo-bin --db-"
"filter>`), da omejite vidnost svojih baz podatkov glede na ime gostitelja. "
"Glejte :ref:`dbfilter`. Uporabite lahko tudi :option:`-d <odoo-bin -d>`, da "
"zagotovite svoj (z vejicami ločen) seznam razpoložljivih baz podatkov za "
"filtriranje, namesto da sistem vse pridobi iz zalednega sistema baze "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:582
msgid ""
"Once your ``db_name`` and ``dbfilter`` are configured and only match a "
"single database per hostname, you should set ``list_db`` configuration "
"option to ``False``, to prevent listing databases entirely, and to block "
"access to the database management screens (this is also exposed as "
"the :option:`--no-database-list <odoo-bin --no-database-list>` command-line "
"option)"
msgstr ""
"Ko sta ``db_name`` in ``dbfilter`` konfigurirana in se ujemata samo z eno "
"bazo podatkov na ime gostitelja, morate možnost konfiguracije ``list_db`` "
"nastaviti na ``False``, da preprečite izpis baz podatkov v celoti in "
"blokirate dostop do zaslonov za upravljanje baz podatkov (to je "
"izpostavljeno tudi kot možnost ukazne vrstice :option:`--no-database-list "
"<odoo-bin --no-database-list>`)"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:588
msgid ""
"Make sure the PostgreSQL user (:option:`--db_user <odoo-bin --db_user>`) is "
"*not* a super-user, and that your databases are owned by a different user. "
"For example they could be owned by the ``postgres`` super-user if you are "
"using a dedicated non-privileged ``db_user``. See also :ref:`setup/deploy/"
"odoo`."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da uporabnik PostgreSQL (:option:`--db_user <odoo-bin --"
"db_user>`) *ni* super-uporabnik in da so vaše baze podatkov v lasti drugega "
"uporabnika. Lahko bi bile na primer v lasti super-uporabnika ``postgres``, "
"če uporabljate namenskega neprivilegiranega ``db_user``. Glejte tudi "
":ref:`setup/deploy/odoo`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:593
msgid ""
"Keep installations updated by regularly installing the latest builds, either "
"via GitHub or by downloading the latest version from https://www.odoo.com/"
"page/download or http://nightly.odoo.com"
msgstr ""
"Posodabljajte namestitve tako, da redno nameščate najnovejše gradnje, bodisi "
"prek GitHuba ali s prenosom najnovejše različice s https://www.odoo.com/page/"
"download ali http://nightly.odoo.com"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:597
msgid ""
"Configure your server in multi-process mode with proper limits matching your "
"typical usage (memory/CPU/timeouts). See also :ref:`builtin_server`."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte svoj strežnik v večprocesnem načinu z ustreznimi omejitvami, "
"ki ustrezajo vaši običajni uporabi (pomnilnik/procesor/časovne omejitve). "
"Glejte tudi :ref:`builtin_server`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:600
msgid ""
"Run Odoo behind a web server providing HTTPS termination with a valid SSL "
"certificate, in order to prevent eavesdropping on cleartext communications. "
"SSL certificates are cheap, and many free options exist. Configure the web "
"proxy to limit the size of requests, set appropriate timeouts, and then "
"enable the :option:`proxy mode <odoo-bin --proxy-mode>` option. See "
"also :ref:`https_proxy`."
msgstr ""
"Zaženite Odoo za spletnim strežnikom, ki zagotavlja prekinitev HTTPS z "
"veljavnim certifikatom SSL, da preprečite prisluškovanje komunikacijam v "
"navadnem besedilu. Certifikati SSL so poceni in obstaja veliko brezplačnih "
"možnosti. Konfigurirajte spletni posrednik, da omeji velikost zahtev, "
"nastavi ustrezne časovne omejitve in nato omogočite možnost :option:`proxy "
"mode <odoo-bin --proxy-mode>`. Glejte tudi :ref:`https_proxy`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:607
msgid ""
"If you need to allow remote SSH access to your servers, make sure to set a "
"strong password for **all** accounts, not just `root`. It is strongly "
"recommended to entirely disable password-based authentication, and only "
"allow public key authentication. Also consider restricting access via a VPN, "
"allowing only trusted IPs in the firewall, and/or running a brute-force "
"detection system such as `fail2ban` or equivalent."
msgstr ""
"Če morate dovoliti oddaljen SSH dostop do vaših strežnikov, poskrbite, da "
"nastavite močno geslo za **vse** račune, ne le za `root`. Močno priporočamo, "
"da popolnoma onemogočite preverjanje pristnosti z geslom in dovolite le "
"preverjanje pristnosti z javnim ključem. Prav tako razmislite o omejevanju "
"dostopa prek VPN-ja, dovoljevanju le zaupanja vrednih IP-jev v požarnem zidu "
"in/ali zagonu sistema za zaznavanje napadov z grobo silo, kot je `fail2ban` "
"ali enakovreden."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:613
msgid ""
"Consider installing appropriate rate-limiting on your proxy or firewall, to "
"prevent brute-force attacks and denial of service attacks. See "
"also :ref:`login_brute_force` for specific measures."
msgstr ""
"Razmislite o namestitvi ustreznega omejevanja hitrosti na vašem proxy ali "
"požarnem zidu, da preprečite napade z grobo silo in napade za zavrnitev "
"storitve. Glejte tudi :ref:`login_brute_force` za posebne ukrepe."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:617
msgid ""
"Many network providers provide automatic mitigation for Distributed Denial "
"of Service attacks (DDOS), but this is often an optional service, so you "
"should consult with them."
msgstr ""
"Številni ponudniki omrežij zagotavljajo samodejno blaženje za napade "
"distribuirane zavrnitve storitve (DDOS), vendar je to pogosto izbirna "
"storitev, zato se posvetujte z njimi."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:621
msgid ""
"Whenever possible, host your public-facing demo/test/staging instances on "
"different machines than the production ones. And apply the same security "
"precautions as for production."
msgstr ""
"Kadar je to mogoče, gostite vaše javno dostopne demo/testne/vmesne primerke "
"na drugih strojih kot produkcijske. In uporabite enake varnostne ukrepe kot "
"za produkcijo."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:625
msgid ""
"If your public-facing Odoo server has access to sensitive internal network "
"resources or services (e.g. via a private VLAN), implement appropriate "
"firewall rules to protect those internal resources. This will ensure that "
"the Odoo server cannot be used accidentally (or as a result of malicious "
"user actions) to access or disrupt those internal resources. Typically this "
"can be done by applying an outbound default DENY rule on the firewall, then "
"only explicitly authorizing access to internal resources that the Odoo "
"server needs to access. `Systemd IP traffic access control <http://"
"0pointer.net/blog/ip-accounting-and-access-lists-with-systemd.html>`_ may "
"also be useful to implement per-process network access control."
msgstr ""
"Če ima vaš javno dostopni strežnik Odoo dostop do občutljivih virov ali "
"storitev notranjega omrežja (npr. prek zasebnega VLAN-a), uvedite ustrezna "
"pravila požarnega zidu za zaščito teh notranjih virov. To bo zagotovilo, da "
"strežnika Odoo ni mogoče uporabiti po naključju (ali kot posledica "
"zlonamernih dejanj uporabnika) za dostop ali motenje teh notranjih virov. To "
"je običajno mogoče storiti z uporabo privzetega odhodnega pravila DENY na "
"požarnem zidu in nato le izrecnim pooblaščanjem dostopa do notranjih virov, "
"do katerih mora strežnik Odoo dostopati. `Systemd nadzor dostopa do IP "
"prometa <http://0pointer.net/blog/ip-accounting-and-access-lists-with-"
"systemd.html>`_ je lahko prav tako uporaben za izvajanje nadzora omrežnega "
"dostopa po procesih."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:636
msgid ""
"If your public-facing Odoo server is behind a Web Application Firewall, a "
"load-balancer, a transparent DDoS protection service (like CloudFlare) or a "
"similar network-level device, you may wish to avoid direct access to the "
"Odoo system. It is generally difficult to keep the endpoint IP addresses of "
"your Odoo servers secret. For example they can appear in web server logs "
"when querying public systems, or in the headers of emails posted from Odoo. "
"In such a situation you may want to configure your firewall so that the "
"endpoints are not accessible publicly except from the specific IP addresses "
"of your WAF, load-balancer or proxy service. Service providers like "
"CloudFlare usually maintain a public list of their IP address ranges for "
"this purpose."
msgstr ""
"Če je vaš javno dostopni strežnik Odoo za požarnim zidom spletnih aplikacij, "
"porazdelilnikom obremenitve, pregledno storitvijo zaščite pred DDoS (kot je "
"CloudFlare) ali podobno napravo na ravni omrežja, se boste morda želeli "
"izogniti neposrednemu dostopu do sistema Odoo. Na splošno je težko ohraniti "
"skrivnost naslovov IP končnih točk vaših strežnikov Odoo. Lahko se na primer "
"pojavijo v dnevnikih spletnih strežnikov pri poizvedovanju javnih sistemov "
"ali v glavah e-poštnih sporočil, objavljenih iz Odoo. V takšni situaciji "
"boste morda želeli konfigurirati požarni zid tako, da končne točke niso "
"javno dostopne, razen z določenih naslovov IP vašega WAF, porazdelilnika "
"obremenitve ali proxy storitve. Ponudniki storitev, kot je CloudFlare, "
"običajno vzdržujejo javni seznam svojih obsegov naslovov IP za ta namen."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:647
msgid ""
"If you are hosting multiple customers, isolate customer data and files from "
"each other using containers or appropriate \"jail\" techniques."
msgstr ""
"Če gostite več strank, izolirajte podatke in datoteke strank med seboj z "
"uporabo vsebnikov ali ustreznih tehnik \"zapora\"."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:650
msgid ""
"Setup daily backups of your databases and filestore data, and copy them to a "
"remote archiving server that is not accessible from the server itself."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite dnevne varnostne kopije vaših podatkovnih baz in podatkov "
"datotečnega skladišča ter jih kopirajte na oddaljeni arhivski strežnik, ki "
"ni dostopen s samega strežnika."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:653
msgid ""
"Deploying Odoo on Linux is strongly recommended over Windows. Should you "
"choose nevertheless to deploy on a Windows platform, a thorough security "
"hardening review of the server should be conducted and is outside of the "
"scope of this guide."
msgstr ""
"Namestitev Odoo na Linux je močno priporočljiva pred Windows. Če se kljub "
"temu odločite za namestitev na platformi Windows, je treba izvesti temeljit "
"pregled varnostne utrditve strežnika, kar je zunaj obsega tega vodnika."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:661
msgid "Blocking Brute Force Attacks"
msgstr "Blokiranje napadov z grobo silo"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:663
msgid ""
"For internet-facing deployments, brute force attacks on user passwords are "
"very common, and this threat should not be neglected for Odoo servers. Odoo "
"emits a log entry whenever a login attempt is performed, and reports the "
"result: success or failure, along with the target login and source IP."
msgstr ""
"Za namestitve, dostopne prek interneta, so napadi z grobo silo na "
"uporabniška gesla zelo pogosti in ta grožnja ne sme biti zanemarjena za "
"strežnike Odoo. Odoo odda dnevniški vnos vsakič, ko je izveden poskus "
"prijave, in poroča o rezultatu: uspeh ali neuspeh skupaj s ciljno prijavo in "
"izvornim IP-jem."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:667
msgid "The log entries will have the following form."
msgstr "Dnevniški vnosi bodo imeli naslednjo obliko."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:669
msgid "Failed login::"
msgstr "Neuspešna prijava::"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:673
msgid "Successful login::"
msgstr "Uspešna prijava::"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:678
msgid ""
"These logs can be easily analyzed by an intrusion prevention system such as "
"`fail2ban`."
msgstr ""
"Te dnevnike lahko enostavno analizira sistem za preprečevanje vdorov, kot je "
"`fail2ban`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:680
msgid ""
"For example, the following fail2ban filter definition should match a failed "
"login::"
msgstr ""
"Na primer, naslednja definicija filtra fail2ban bi se morala ujemati z "
"neuspešno prijavo::"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:687
msgid ""
"This could be used with a jail definition to block the attacking IP on "
"HTTP(S)."
msgstr ""
"To bi bilo mogoče uporabiti z definicijo zapora za blokiranje napadalnega IP-"
"ja na HTTP(S)."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:689
msgid ""
"Here is what it could look like for blocking the IP for 15 minutes when 10 "
"failed login attempts are detected from the same IP within 1 minute::"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je, kako bi lahko izgledalo za blokiranje IP-ja za 15 minut, ko je z "
"istega IP-ja v 1 minuti zaznanih 10 neuspešnih poskusov prijave::"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:703
msgid "Database Manager Security"
msgstr "Varnost upravitelja podatkovne baze"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:705
msgid ":ref:`setup/deploy/odoo` mentioned ``admin_passwd`` in passing."
msgstr ":ref:`setup/deploy/odoo` je omenil ``admin_passwd`` mimogrede."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:707
msgid ""
"This setting is used on all database management screens (to create, delete, "
"dump or restore databases)."
msgstr ""
"Toto nastavení se používá na všech obrazovkách správy databází (pro "
"vytváření, mazání, výpis nebo obnovení databází)."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:710
msgid ""
"If the management screens must not be accessible at all, you should set "
"``list_db`` configuration option to ``False``, to block access to all the "
"database selection and management screens."
msgstr ""
"Pokud obrazovky správy nemají být vůbec přístupné, měli byste nastavit "
"konfigurační možnost ``list_db`` na ``False``, abyste zablokovali přístup ke "
"všem obrazovkám výběru a správy databází."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:716
msgid ""
"It is strongly recommended to disable the Database Manager for any internet-"
"facing system! It is meant as a development/demo tool, to make it easy to "
"quickly create and manage databases. It is not designed for use in "
"production, and may even expose dangerous features to attackers. It is also "
"not designed to handle large databases, and may trigger memory limits."
msgstr ""
"Důrazně se doporučuje zakázat Správce databází pro jakýkoli systém vystavený "
"internetu! Je určen jako vývojový/demo nástroj pro snadné a rychlé vytváření "
"a správu databází. Není navržen pro použití v produkci a může útočníkům "
"dokonce odhalit nebezpečné funkce. Také není navržen pro práci s velkými "
"databázemi a může způsobit dosažení paměťových limitů."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:722
msgid ""
"On production systems, database management operations should always be "
"performed by the system administrator, including provisioning of new "
"databases and automated backups."
msgstr ""
"V produkčních systémech by operace správy databází měl vždy provádět správce "
"systému, včetně zřizování nových databází a automatizovaných záloh."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:725
msgid ""
"Be sure to setup an appropriate ``db_name`` parameter (and optionally, "
"``dbfilter`` too) so that the system can determine the target database for "
"each request, otherwise users will be blocked as they won't be allowed to "
"choose the database themselves."
msgstr ""
"Ujistěte se, že jste nastavili vhodný parametr ``db_name`` (a volitelně také "
"``dbfilter``), aby systém mohl určit cílovou databázi pro každý požadavek, "
"jinak budou uživatelé zablokováni, protože nebudou moci vybrat databázi sami."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:730
msgid ""
"If the management screens must only be accessible from a selected set of "
"machines, use the proxy server's features to block access to all routes "
"starting with ``/web/database`` except (maybe) ``/web/database/selector`` "
"which displays the database-selection screen."
msgstr ""
"Pokud mají být obrazovky správy přístupné pouze z vybrané sady strojů, "
"použijte funkce proxy serveru k zablokování přístupu ke všem cestám "
"začínajícím ``/web/database`` s výjimkou (možná) ``/web/database/selector``, "
"která zobrazuje obrazovku výběru databáze."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:734
msgid ""
"If the database-management screen should be left accessible, the "
"``admin_passwd`` setting must be changed from its ``admin`` default: this "
"password is checked before allowing database-alteration operations."
msgstr ""
"Pokud má zůstat obrazovka správy databází přístupná, musí být nastavení "
"``admin_passwd`` změněno z výchozí hodnoty ``admin``: toto heslo je "
"kontrolováno před povolením operací měnících databázi."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:738
msgid "It should be stored securely, and should be generated randomly e.g."
msgstr ""
"Mělo by být bezpečně uloženo a mělo by být generováno náhodně, například."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:744
msgid "which generates a 32-character pseudorandom printable string."
msgstr "což vygeneruje 32znakový pseudonáhodný tisknutelný řetězec."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:747
msgid "Reset the master password"
msgstr "Resetovat hlavní heslo"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:749
msgid ""
"There may be instances where the master password is misplaced, or "
"compromised, and needs to be reset. The following process is for system "
"administrators of an Odoo on-premise database detailing how to manually "
"reset and re-encrypt the master password."
msgstr ""
"Mohou nastat situace, kdy je hlavní heslo ztraceno nebo kompromitováno a je "
"třeba jej resetovat. Následující postup je pro správce systému databáze Odoo "
"on-premise a podrobně popisuje, jak ručně resetovat a znovu zašifrovat "
"hlavní heslo."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:754
msgid ":doc:`../odoo_accounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`../odoo_accounts`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:756
msgid ""
"When creating a new on-premise database, a random master password is "
"generated. Odoo recommends using this password to secure the database. This "
"password is implemented by default, so there is a secure master password for "
"any Odoo on-premise deployment."
msgstr ""
"Při vytváření nové databáze on-premise je vygenerováno náhodné hlavní heslo. "
"Odoo doporučuje použít toto heslo k zabezpečení databáze. Toto heslo je "
"implementováno ve výchozím nastavení, takže existuje bezpečné hlavní heslo "
"pro jakékoli nasazení Odoo on-premise."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:761
msgid ""
"When creating an Odoo on-premise database the installation is accessible to "
"anyone on the internet, until this password is set to secure the database."
msgstr ""
"Při vytváření databáze Odoo on-premise je instalace přístupná komukoli na "
"internetu, dokud není toto heslo nastaveno k zabezpečení databáze."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:764
msgid ""
"The master password is specified in the Odoo configuration file (`odoo.conf` "
"or `odoorc` (hidden file)). The Odoo master password is needed to modify, "
"create, or delete a database through the graphical user interface (GUI)."
msgstr ""
"Hlavní heslo je specifikováno v konfiguračním souboru Odoo (`odoo.conf` nebo "
"`odoorc` (skrytý soubor)). Hlavní heslo Odoo je potřeba k úpravě, vytvoření "
"nebo smazání databáze prostřednictvím grafického uživatelského rozhraní "
"(GUI)."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:769
msgid "Locate configuration file"
msgstr "Najít konfigurační soubor"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:771
msgid ""
"First, open the Odoo configuration file (`odoo.conf` or `odoorc` (hidden "
"file))."
msgstr ""
"Nejprve otevřete konfigurační soubor Odoo (`odoo.conf` nebo `odoorc` (skrytý "
"soubor))."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:775
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/packages.rst:148
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:70
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:133
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:158
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:180
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:208
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:239
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:328
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:397
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:460
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Windows"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:777
msgid ""
"The configuration file is located at: `c:\\\\ProgramFiles\\\\Odoo{VERSION}\\"
"\\server\\\\odoo.conf`"
msgstr ""
"Konfigurační soubor se nachází na: `c:\\\\ProgramFiles\\\\Odoo{VERSION}\\"
"\\server\\\\odoo.conf`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:779
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/packages.rst:25
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:52
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:129
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:152
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:174
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:199
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:228
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:271
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:388
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:450
msgid "Linux"
msgstr "Linux"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:781
msgid ""
"Depending on how Odoo is installed on the Linux machine, the configuration "
"file is located in one of two different places:"
msgstr ""
"V závislosti na tom, jak je Odoo nainstalováno na počítači s Linuxem, se "
"konfigurační soubor nachází na jednom ze dvou různých míst:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:784
msgid "Package installation: `/etc/odoo.conf`"
msgstr "Namestitev paketa: `/etc/odoo.conf`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:785
msgid "Source installation: `~/.odoorc`"
msgstr "Namestitev iz izvorne kode: `~/.odoorc`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:788
msgid "Change old password"
msgstr "Sprememba starega gesla"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:790
msgid ""
"Once the appropriate file has been opened, proceed to modify the old "
"password in the configuration file to a temporary password."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ustrezna datoteka odprta, spremenite staro geslo v konfiguracijski "
"datoteki na začasno geslo."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:795
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:843
msgid "Graphical user interface"
msgstr "Grafični uporabniški vmesnik"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:797
msgid ""
"After locating the configuration file, open it using a (:abbr:`GUI "
"(graphical user interface)`). This can be achieved by simply double clicking "
"on the file. Then, the device should have a default :abbr:`GUI (graphical "
"user interface)` to open the file with."
msgstr ""
"Po tem, ko najdete konfiguracijsko datoteko, jo odprite z :abbr:`GUI "
"(grafični uporabniški vmesnik)`. To dosežete tako, da dvakrat kliknete na "
"datoteko. Naprava bi morala imeti privzet :abbr:`GUI (grafični uporabniški "
"vmesnik)`, s katerim se datoteka odpre."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:801
msgid ""
"Next, modify the master password line `admin_passwd = $pbkdf2-sha…` to "
"`admin_passwd = newpassword1234`, for example. This password can be "
"anything, as long as it is saved temporarily. Make sure to modify all "
"characters after the `=`."
msgstr ""
"Nato spremenite vrstico glavnega gesla `admin_passwd = $pbkdf2-sha…` v "
"`admin_passwd = newpassword1234`, na primer. To geslo je lahko karkoli, "
"dokler je začasno shranjeno. Prepričajte se, da spremenite vse znake za "
"znakom `=`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:806
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:825
msgid ""
"The line appears like this: `admin_passwd = $pbkdf2-"
"sh39dji295.59mptrfW.9z6HkA$w9j9AMVmKAP17OosCqDxDv2hjsvzlLpF8Rra8I7p/"
"b573hji540mk/.3ek0lg%kvkol6k983mkf/40fjki79m`"
msgstr ""
"Vrstica izgleda takole: `admin_passwd = $pbkdf2-"
"sh39dji295.59mptrfW.9z6HkA$w9j9AMVmKAP17OosCqDxDv2hjsvzlLpF8Rra8I7p/"
"b573hji540mk/.3ek0lg%kvkol6k983mkf/40fjki79m`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:810
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:829
msgid "The modified line appears like this: `admin_passwd = newpassword1234`"
msgstr "Spremenjena vrstica izgleda takole: `admin_passwd = newpassword1234`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:812
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:852
msgid "Command-line interface"
msgstr "Vmesnik ukazne vrstice"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:814
msgid ""
"Modify the master password line using the following Unix command detailed "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite vrstico glavnega gesla z naslednjim Unix ukazom, opisanim spodaj."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:816
msgid ""
"Connect to the Odoo server's terminal via Secure Shell (SSH) protocol, and "
"edit the configuration file. To modify the configuration file, enter the "
"following command: :command:`sudo nano /etc/odoo.conf`"
msgstr ""
"Povežite se z terminalom strežnika Odoo preko protokola Secure Shell (SSH) "
"in uredite konfiguracijsko datoteko. Za spremembo konfiguracijske datoteke "
"vnesite naslednji ukaz: :command:`sudo nano /etc/odoo.conf`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:820
msgid ""
"After opening the configuration file, modify the master password line "
"`admin_passwd = $pbkdf2-sha…` to `admin_passwd = newpassword1234`. This "
"password can be anything, as long as it is saved temporarily. Make sure to "
"modify all characters after the `=`."
msgstr ""
"Po odprtju konfiguracijske datoteke spremenite vrstico glavnega gesla "
"`admin_passwd = $pbkdf2-sha…` v `admin_passwd = newpassword1234`. To geslo "
"je lahko karkoli, dokler je začasno shranjeno. Prepričajte se, da spremenite "
"vse znake za znakom `=`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:832
msgid ""
"It is essential that the password is changed to something else, rather than "
"triggering a new password reset by adding a semicolon `;` at the beginning "
"of the line. This ensures the database is secure throughout the entire "
"password reset process."
msgstr ""
"Bistveno je, da se geslo spremeni v nekaj drugega, namesto da se sproži novo "
"ponastavitev gesla z dodajanjem podpičja `;` na začetek vrstice. To "
"zagotavlja, da je baza podatkov varna med celotnim procesom ponastavitve "
"gesla."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:837
msgid "Restart Odoo server"
msgstr "Ponovni zagon strežnika Odoo"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:839
msgid ""
"After setting the temporary password, a restart of the Odoo server is "
"**required**."
msgstr ""
"Po nastavitvi začasnega gesla je **obvezen** ponovni zagon strežnika Odoo."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:845
msgid ""
"To restart the Odoo server, first, type `services` into the "
"Windows :guilabel:`Search` bar. Then, select the :guilabel:`Services` "
"application, and scroll down to the :guilabel:`Odoo` service."
msgstr ""
"Za ponovni zagon strežnika Odoo najprej v iskalno vrstico "
"Windows :guilabel:`Iskanje` vnesite `services`. Nato izberite "
"aplikacijo :guilabel:`Storitve` in se pomaknite navzdol do "
"storitve :guilabel:`Odoo`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:849
msgid ""
"Next, right click on :guilabel:`Odoo`, and select :guilabel:`Start` "
"or :guilabel:`Restart`. This action manually restarts the Odoo server."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite z desno tipko miške na :guilabel:`Odoo` in "
"izberite :guilabel:`Začni` ali :guilabel:`Ponovni zagon`. To dejanje ročno "
"znova zažene strežnik Odoo."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:854
msgid ""
"Restart the Odoo server by typing the command: :command:`sudo service odoo15 "
"restart`"
msgstr ""
"Znova zaženite strežnik Odoo tako, da vnesete ukaz: :command:`sudo service "
"odoo15 restart`"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:857
msgid ""
"Change the number after `odoo` to fit the specific version the server is "
"running on."
msgstr ""
"Spremenite številko za `odoo`, da ustreza določeni različici, na kateri teče "
"strežnik."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:860
msgid "Use web interface to re-encrypt password"
msgstr "Uporabi spletni vmesnik za ponovno šifriranje gesla"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:862
msgid ""
"First, navigate to `/web/database/manager` or `http://server_ip:port/web/"
"database/manager` in a browser."
msgstr ""
"Najprej v brskalniku odpri `/web/database/manager` ali `http://"
"server_ip:port/web/database/manager`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:866
msgid ""
"Replace `server_ip` with the IP address of the database. Replace `port` with "
"the numbered port the database is accessible from."
msgstr ""
"Zamenjaj `server_ip` z IP-naslovom podatkovne baze. Zamenjaj `port` s "
"številko vrat, prek katerih je podatkovna baza dostopna."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/deploy.rst:869
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Set Master Password`, and type in the previously-"
"selected temporary password into the :guilabel:`Master Password` field. "
"Following this step, type in a :guilabel:`New Master Password`. "
"The :guilabel:`New Master Password` is hashed (or encrypted), once "
"the :guilabel:`Continue` button is clicked."
msgstr ""
"Nato klikni :guilabel:`Set Master Password` in v polje :guilabel:`Master "
"Password` vnesi prej izbrano začasno geslo. Po tem koraku "
