#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:428
msgid "Running Odoo"
msgstr "Zagon Odooja"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:430
msgid ""
"Once all dependencies are set up, Odoo can be launched by running `odoo-"
"bin`, the command-line interface of the server. It is located at the root of "
"the Odoo Community directory."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse odvisnosti nastavljene, lahko zaženete Odoo z zagonom `odoo-bin`, "
"vmesnika ukazne vrstice strežnika. Nahaja se v korenu imenika Odoo Community."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:433
msgid ""
"To configure the server, either specify :ref:`command-line arguments "
"<reference/cmdline/server>` or a :ref:`configuration file <reference/cmdline/"
"config>`."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo strežnika navedite :ref:`argumente ukazne vrstice "
"<reference/cmdline/server>` ali :ref:`konfiguracijsko datoteko <reference/"
"cmdline/config>`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:437
msgid ""
"For the Enterprise edition, add the path to the `enterprise` add-ons to the "
"`addons-path` argument. Note that it must come before the other paths in "
"`addons-path` for add-ons to be loaded correctly."
msgstr ""
"Za izdajo Enterprise dodajte pot do dodatkov `enterprise` v argument `addons-"
"path`. Upoštevajte, da mora biti pred ostalimi potmi v `addons-path`, da se "
"dodatki pravilno naložijo."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:441
msgid "Common necessary configurations are:"
msgstr "Pogoste potrebne konfiguracije so:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:443
msgid "PostgreSQL user and password."
msgstr "Uporabnik in geslo PostgreSQL."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:444
msgid "Custom addon paths beyond the defaults to load custom modules."
msgstr "Poti po meri dodatkov poleg privzetih za nalaganje modulov po meri."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:446
msgid "A typical way to run the server would be:"
msgstr "Običajen način zagona strežnika bi bil:"

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:457
#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:478
msgid ""
"Where `CommunityPath` is the path of the Odoo Community installation, and "
"`mydb` is the name of the PostgreSQL database."
msgstr ""
"Kjer je `CommunityPath` pot namestitve Odoo Community in `mydb` ime "
"podatkovne baze PostgreSQL."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:467
msgid ""
"Where `CommunityPath` is the path of the Odoo Community installation, "
"`dbuser` is the PostgreSQL login, `dbpassword` is the PostgreSQL password, "
"and `mydb` is the name of the PostgreSQL database."
msgstr ""
"Kjer je `CommunityPath` pot namestitve Odoo Community, `dbuser` je prijava "
"PostgreSQL, `dbpassword` je geslo PostgreSQL in `mydb` je ime podatkovne "
"baze PostgreSQL."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:481
msgid ""
"After the server has started (the INFO log `odoo.modules.loading: Modules "
"loaded.` is printed), open http://localhost:8069 in a web browser and log "
"into the Odoo database with the base administrator account: use `admin` as "
"the email and, again, `admin` as the password."
msgstr ""
"Ko se strežnik zažene (izpiše se dnevnik INFO `odoo.modules.loading: Modules "
"loaded.`), odprite http://localhost:8069 v spletnem brskalniku in se "
"prijavite v podatkovno bazo Odoo z osnovnim skrbniškim računom: uporabite "
"`admin` kot e-poštni naslov in ponovno `admin` kot geslo."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:486
msgid ""
"From there, create and manage new :doc:`users <../../applications/general/"
"users>`."
msgstr ""
"Od tam ustvarite in upravljajte nove :doc:`uporabnike <../../applications/"
"general/users>`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:487
msgid ""
"The user account used to log into Odoo's web interface differs from "
"the :option:`--db_user <odoo-bin -r>` CLI argument."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniški račun, uporabljen za prijavo v spletni vmesnik Odooja, se "
"razlikuje od argumenta CLI :option:`--db_user <odoo-bin -r>`."

#: ../../content/administration/on_premise/source.rst:491
msgid ""
":doc:`The list of CLI arguments for odoo-bin </developer/reference/cli>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Seznam argumentov CLI za odoo-bin </developer/reference/cli>`"

